# Place your AWS TLS certificate files here before building.
# See firmware/mqtt/README.md for instructions.
#
# Required files (NOT committed to git — add to .gitignore):
#   AmazonRootCA1.pem   — AWS Root CA (public, download from amazontrust.com)
#   device.crt          — Your device certificate from AWS IoT Core
#   device.key          — Your device private key (keep secret!)
